<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:17:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>举重——中国名将李娜卫冕61公斤级金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-li-fabin-wins-mens-61kg-gold-2024-08-07/</link><description>中国选手李发斌在周三的巴黎奥运会上以310公斤的总举重成绩卫冕61公斤级奥运会举重冠军，距离打破自己保持的世界纪录仅一步之遥。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-li-fabin-wins-mens-61kg-gold-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>巴西面临的中国家禽出口限制减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-facing-fewer-chinese-restrictions-poultry-exports-2024-08-07/</link><description>中国食品土畜进出口商会周三表示，自8月2日起对巴西家禽销售的限制仅适用于南里奥格兰德州的产品，该州上个月爆发了新城疫疫情。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-facing-fewer-chinese-restrictions-poultry-exports-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-勒布伦兄弟带领法国队闯入团体半决赛迎战中国队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-men-beat-korea-swiftie-kaufmann-sends-germanys-women-into-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三，法国小将菲利克斯·勒布伦在四天内第二次战胜巴西选手乌戈·卡尔德拉诺，拿下关键一分，帮助法国队击败巴西队，晋级乒乓球男子团体赛半决赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:48:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-men-beat-korea-swiftie-kaufmann-sends-germanys-women-into-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>西门子能源首席执行官呼吁亚洲风电公司进入欧洲进行公平竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</link><description>西门子能源首席执行官周三表示，活跃在欧洲的中国和西方风力涡轮机制造商必须在相同的市场条件下销售产品，以创造公平竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>投资者在中国针对恒大集团提出清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三提交的一份股票文件显示，一名投资者已向中国法院提交请愿书，要求清算负债累累的房地产开发商中国恒大的一个主要部门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>彪马因货运成本高、中国市场低迷而缩小了财年利润前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-narrows-fy-core-profit-outlook-2024-08-07/</link><description>德国运动服装制造商彪马周三缩小了全年核心利润预期，导致其股价短暂跌至 2018 年低点，理由是货运成本上升、汇率不利以及中国消费者信心持续低迷。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-narrows-fy-core-profit-outlook-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国在南海黄岩岛附近举行联合作战巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>南部战区在微信应用程序上发帖称，中国军队周三在南海黄岩岛附近组织海空联合作战巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡星展银行上调 2024 年预期，因强劲的财富流动推动利润增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</link><description>新加坡最大的银行星展集团受益于蓬勃发展的财富业务，将资产和费用收入推至创纪录水平，周三，星展集团上调了全年利润指引。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国进口恢复增长但出口放缓引发前景担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</link><description>7月份，中国的出口增长速度为三个月来最慢，低于预期，加剧了人们对庞大制造业前景的担忧，而在美国预期的科技限制措施之前急于增加芯片供应，导致进口增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:52:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国终止多国海上演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>菲律宾周三表示，三艘中国海军舰艇尾随菲律宾与加拿大、美国和澳大利亚在有争议的南海海域举行的联合军事演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，中国恒大清算人对普华永道提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周二报道，陷入困境的房地产巨头中国恒大集团的清算人已对普华永道采取法律行动，指责其在为集团工作时“疏忽”和“失实陈述”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>面对中国的“胁迫”，美国将增加澳大利亚的兵力投送</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-us-discuss-greater-defence-cooperation-2024-08-06/</link><description>两国在年度防务会谈后表示，澳大利亚将于明年开始与美国共同制造制导武器，以增加对印太地区盟国的供应，并增加美国在该国的军事存在，包括轰炸机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:14:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-us-discuss-greater-defence-cooperation-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国需求改善，Vans 母公司 VF Corp 第一季度营收降幅小于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>VF Corp 周二公布，由于中国业务改善以及库存水平下降，第一季度营收降幅小于预期，导致其股价在盘后交易中上涨约 7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国学者在美充当外国代理人被判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，一名中国学者被判在美国非法充当外国代理人，他收集了纽约支持中国民主的活动人士的信息，并与北京分享了他的调查结果。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>美澳会谈重点关注中国的“胁迫行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-highlights-growing-us-military-presence-ahead-ausmin-talks-2024-08-06/</link><description>官员称，美国和澳大利亚周二启动了高层会谈，重点讨论中国的“胁迫行为”、AUKUS核潜艇项目和中东日益紧张的局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-highlights-growing-us-military-presence-ahead-ausmin-talks-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>